WEBVTT

00:00:29.328 --> 00:00:31.624
by not having enough fishing.

00:00:31.648 --> 00:00:35.009
So, they decided to do something
nobody expected.

00:00:35.033 --> 00:00:38.394
Instead of spending more time at sea
searching for the last fish,

00:00:38.418 --> 00:00:41.543
they decided to stop fishing completely.

00:00:41.922 --> 00:00:46.102
They created a national park at sea,
a marine reserve.

00:00:46.688 --> 00:00:49.981
When we came back to Cabo Pulmo
ten years later,

00:00:50.473 --> 00:00:51.677
this is what we saw.

00:00:53.106 --> 00:00:55.022
What had been an underwater wasteland

00:00:55.046 --> 00:00:58.752
had become a kaleidoscope
of color and life.

00:00:58.776 --> 00:01:01.529
We saw it come back to its pristine state